The '''Book of Battle''' is a spellbook containing spells helpful for melee combat.

==Spells==
{{spellbook|book of Battle}}

==History==
*This book was re-added in [[0.31]] with a different spell set.
*Prior to [[0.26]], this was a book of [[Charms]] spells, containing [[Infusion]], [[Shroud of Golubria]], [[Song of Slaying]], [[Ozocubu's Armour]] and [[Spectral Weapon]]. It was the starting book for [[Skald]]s. It was removed along with the [[Charms]] school.
*The Book of Battle was added in [[0.13]].

